mber\">1\u003C/span>D·M·S·\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Caius · Iulius · Eutych\n                    ·us\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Caius\">C\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Iulius\">IULIUS\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Eutych\n                    ·us\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Eutych\n                    ·us\">EUTYCH\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>·US\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>·VIXIT·AN·XXXX·\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>·UXOR·B·MER·FEC·\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000704_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2017-07-01\" src=\"ISic000704_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000704.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2017-07-01\" src=\"ISic000704-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000704_copy2_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo students of Liceo Lazzaro\" src=\"ISic000704_copy2_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000704_copy2.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo students of Liceo Lazzaro\" src=\"ISic000704_copy2-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000704_rear_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo students of Liceo Lazzaro\" src=\"ISic000704_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000704_rear.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo students of Liceo Lazzaro\" src=\"ISic000704_rear-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text from photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Sacred to the spirits of the underworld. Gaius Iulius Eutychus lived for 40 years. His wife made this for a well deserving man.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>Consacrato agli Dei Mani | Caius Iulius Eutychus | Visse per 40 anni | La moglie pose per (il marito) meritevole\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Whether Gaius Iulius Eutychus was a freedman (former slave) or freeborn we cannot tell, but the absence of a father’s name perhaps suggests the former. The Greek name \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Εὐτύχης\u003C/span> (‘good fortune’) is very common, in Sicily and across the Greek world. The inscription follows a very standard form for Latin epitaphs, although the use of interpuncts is excessive and is relatively unusual in appearing at the start and end of lines, including therefore mid-word/name (start of line 3).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 1989.0341g \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1989 170 no.37 fig.39 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 97 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> \u003Cp> Line 1  30-35  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not measured  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[241,244,247,250,253,255,258,261,264],{"id":242,"html":243},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>D(is) · m(anibus) · s(acrum) · \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>· \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Caius · Iulius · Eutych\n                    ·us\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Caius\">C(aius)\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Iulius\">Iulius\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Eutych\n                    ·us\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Eutych\n                    ·us\">Eutyc