"5616px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo students of Liceo Lazzaro\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000704_rear.jpg\" height=\"3744px\" width=\"5616px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo students of Liceo Lazzaro\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n        \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>D\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>is\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>m\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>anibus\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>s\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>acrum\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>C\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>aius\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/name> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cname>Iulius\u003C/name> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cname>\u003Cw>Eutych\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\" break=\"no\"/>\u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g>us\u003C/w>\u003C/name>\u003C/persName> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> vixit \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>an\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>nos\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cnum value=\"40\">XXXX\u003C/num> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>\u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> uxor \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>b\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ene\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>mer\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>enti\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>fec\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>it\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cg ref=\"#interpunct\">·\u003C/g>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text from photograph\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>Sacred to the spirits of the underworld. Gaius Iulius Eutychus lived for 40 years. His wife made this for a well deserving man.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\">\n                \u003Cp>Consacrato agli Dei Mani | Caius Iulius Eutychus | Visse per 40 anni | La moglie pose per (il marito) meritevole\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n                \u003Cp>Whether Gaius Iulius Eutychus was a freedman (former slave) or freeborn we cannot tell, but the\n                    absence of a father’s name perhaps suggests the former. The Greek name \u003Cforeign xml:lang=\"grc\">Εὐτύχης\u003C/foreign> (‘good fortune’) is\n                    very common, in Sicily and across the Greek world. The inscription follows a very standard form for Latin epitaphs, although the use of interpuncts is excessive and is relatively unusual in appearing at the start and end of lines, including therefore mid-word/name (start of line 3).\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"AE\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>1989.0341g\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/R46KDTZX\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manganaro\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1989\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>170 no.37 fig.39\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/EZMBJ6GN\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IMusCatania\">\n                         \u003Cauthor>Korhonen\u003C/author>\n                         \u003Cdate>2004\u003C/date> \n                        \u003CcitedRange>97\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/2EUC82DH\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl/>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
